Spell:Pre-emptive Strike

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search
Pre-emptive Strike
Spell Information
School
Pip Cost0
Accuracy100%
Type / 
Spell Description
Deals 50 Balance Damage to target and applies a -75 Damage Charm if target has 4 or more Pips
Training Sources
This Spell cannot be trained
This Spell is to available to the Balance Ninja Pig Beastmoon Form during Beastmoon events.


Beastmoon Form Caster
  • Balance Ninja Pig

Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:SpellInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to Pre-emptive Strike should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to Pre-emptive Strike in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
